Sentencas: A kind of cathode material of Pr1-xSrx FeO3 (x=0-0.5) for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs) was prepared by the coprecipitation method.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of Pr1-xSrxFeO3 cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Crystal structure, thermal expansion, electrical conductivity and electrochemical performance of the Pr1-xSrxFeO3 perovskite oxide cathodes were studied by different methods.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of Pr1-xSrxFeO3 cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The results revealed that Pr1-xSrxFeO3 exhibited similar orthorhombic structure from x = 0. 1 to 0.3 and took cubic structure when x = 0.4-0.5.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of Pr1-xSrxFeO3 cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The unit cell volume decreased and the thermal expansion coefficient (TEC) of the materials increased as the strontium content increased.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of Pr1-xSrxFeO3 cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: When 0 < x <= 0.3, the samples exhibited good thermal expansion compatibility with YSZ electrolyte.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of Pr1-xSrxFeO3 cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity increased with the increasing of doped strontium content.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of Pr1-xSrxFeO3 cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: When x = 0. 3-0.5, the electrical conductivities were higher than 100 S cm(-1).
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of Pr1-xSrxFeO3 cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The conductivity of Pr0.8Sr0.2FeO3 was 78 S cm(-1) at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of Pr1-xSrxFeO3 cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Compared with the La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 cathode, Pr0.8Sr0.2FeO3 showed higher polarization current density and lower polarization resistance (0.2038 Omega cm(2)).
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of Pr1-xSrxFeO3 cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The value of I-0 for Pr0.8Sr0.2FeO3 at 800 degrees C is 123.6 mA cm(-2).
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of Pr1-xSrxFeO3 cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: It is higher than that of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of Pr1-xSrxFeO3 cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Therefore, Pr1-xSrxFeO3 can be considered as a candidate cathode material for IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of Pr1-xSrxFeO3 cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
